# Project Overview
Our app ZenZone is a study support app. Many students may face problems such as studying alone, getting bored or distracted, reducing focus with Social media, Netflix, YouTube, and games. So our app helps students to  stay focused, manage time and study with others. This also supports SDG 4 – Quality Education because it helps students learn better.
 
# Users needs
Our group collected opinions from many students.
 From their answers, we found common problems. 
Students said they feel bored studying alone, get distracted by YouTube, Netflix, games, have poor time management,want study partners, want motivation and progress tracking.

# Solution
Our solution is the ZenZone study app.The app will give students tools like: 
- study buddy matching
- focus timers
- task tracking
- progress dashboards
- study suggestion
These tools help students study more effectively.

# Key features
The important key factors are studdy buddy matching, timer, goal tracker, progress dashboard, focus mood, study suggestion.
- Study Buddy Matching allows students can find others students who taking  the same course and study together.
- Timer helps students focus for short study sessions.
- Goal Tracker helps students can add tasks and goals to stay organized.
- Progress Dashboard shows study time and productivity statistics.
- Focus Mode blocks distracting apps or websites.
- Study Suggestions suggest study plans based on subjects.

# Target Users
Our app is made for 
- university students
- students studying online
- students who struggle with distractions
- students who want study partners

# SDG 4 Contribution
Our app supports this because it improves learning tools, helps students study better, encourages collaboration,supports productive learning habits.
